{
  "texts": [
    "Finally, these data objects are passed on to other modules.",
    "We simplify the data preparation into three stages:• Data loading: Loading necessary data from the hard disk.",
    "• Data processing: Convert the raw data into modelfriendly data objects by a range of data processing operations.",
    "• Data delivery: Deliver model-friendly data objects to other modules.Among these three stages, data processing is the most complex and feature-rich stage in data preparation.",
    "Therefore, we have established a set of standardized protocols and Fig. 4 The overall architecture of EduStudio developed a series of atomic data operations for data processing (detailed in Section 4.2.1)."
  ]
}